title: Australian Digital Health Agency FHIR Implementation Guide

list.desc: Continuous Integration Build R4  (latest in version control) - Content subject to frequent changes.

Release of the Australian Digital Health Agency FHIR Implementation Guide to support Medicare records in HL7™ FHIR® Release 4 (R4) to support the electronic exchange of health information between individuals, healthcare providers, and the My Health Record system infrastructure in Australia.
